text: DYKA (801 kHz) Radyo Totoo is an AM radio station owned and operated by Kauswagan Broadcasting Corporation, the media arm of the Roman Catholic Diocese of San Jose de Antique. Its studio and transmitter are located at 3/F St.Joseph Center, Gen.
